     <div class="span-24  last">
      <P>Grepdeals is a portal web site which offers the best deals in town and makes the shopping experience more
      easier, affordable and enjoyable. Whether it is products or services, Grepdeals aims at getting the 
      best bargains at your fingertips, by offering user-friendly discount/deal coupons. By simply 
      registering their e-mail addresses, users will get exciting deals everyday to choose from, and purchase
      the same which can be redeemed by using the printed copy of the deal bought.</P>
      <P></P>
      <BR/>
      <P><B>Register as a new user:</B></P>
      <P>1. Click register as a new user
         2. Enter valid email account, password, zipcode
         3. You will receive an email from grepdeals to validate your account
         4. Click the link and you will get into grepdeals deals page</P>
      <P><B>Register as a Merchant:</B></P>
      <P>1. You have to be registered user, Follow the above steps
         2. After Login goto Merchant Signup
         3. Enter all the details in Merchant Signup page
         4. you will receive an email once your request is approved by grepdeals admin</P>
      <P><B>Post an advertisement:</B></P>
      <P>1. Login to grepdeals account, You have to be approved merchant to get into Post Advertisement link
         2. Click on Post Advertisement link
         3. Enter the details into the Title, Subject and upload the photos if any. Describe your advertisement
         4. Click Submit Button
         5. Your post will be emailed to all registered users and also be posted into your Facebook
       </P>
      
